headline: Ahead of TE Connectivity (TEL) Q4 Earnings: Get Ready With Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for TE Connectivity (TEL), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended September 2025.
